Caledonia Plasma Theme Changelog
--------------------------------

*_v1.6.2 Mar 07 2014

-Updated documentation
-Added Euskera, Chinese and Esperanto languages to metadata description
-Little revision in Amarok icon file
-Added an icon for Cantata
-Icon compatibility with new Plasma-nm (version 0.9.3.3)
-Revised slider widget
-Revised Calendar decorations
-Revised icon theme colors
-New chronometer design

*_v1.6.1 Feb 23 2014

-Updated to the new standard icon in KDE Connect
-Added Brazilian Portugese to metadata description
-Fixed some bugs with some icons in Plasma-nm (versions 0.4.2.x)

*_v1.6 Feb 17 2014

-KDE 4.12.2 compatible
-Added more languages in metadata description (Finnish, Russian-RU, generic Russian)
-Added a donation direct access
-Icon support for KDE Connect (thanks to Albert Vaka collaboration with KDE Connect code) - Superior to version 0.4.2
-Great icon support (140 pieces) for Plasma NetworkManagement QML (ethernet, wifi, VPN, mobile networks, airplane mode)
-Revised preferences icons
-Revised KWallet icons
-Revised list item component
-Revised Choqok icon
-Revised Kickoff decoration
-Revised location icons
-Revised SLC icons
-Revised list item decorations
-Revised Record It Now icon

