-Updated Kaffeine icon
-New icons for presence applet (Telepathy)
-New device plug notification icon
-New icon for Amarok
-Added icon support for DiscBurner plasmoid
-Added bubblemon plasmoid support
-Added Fifteen Puzzle plasmoid support
-Added an icon for previewer plasmoid
-Added an icon for location tool
-New icon for Choqok
-New "like" SLC icon
-Calendar icon revised
-New icon for activities
-Added original design for Notes plasmoid
-Activated background to the lockscreen
-Initial support for Plasma NetworkManagement QML
-Revised desktop pager icon

